    {
      "id": "dAbRIVBF7M5u2rzvTwqWG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1688.6024769607814,
      "y": 1530.5343557938318,
      "width": 780.3314208984375,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1997691046,
      "version": 50,
      "versionNonce": 788094502,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783648594727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CP-001 — Systems over Tools        El valor está en el sistema,\nno en la herramienta utilizada para implementarlo.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CP-001 — Systems over Tools        El valor está en el sistema, no en la herramienta utilizada para implementarlo.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q2P8vpuAqkVp0WGB-wa2l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1688.6024769607814,
      "y": 1653.6819770383113,
      "width": 789.6275024414062,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2086235322,
      "version": 41,
      "versionNonce": 565619046,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783648594727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CP-002 — Process over Improvisation        El trabajo repetitivo\ndebe ejecutarse mediante procesos diseñados previamente, no\nmediante improvisación constante.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CP-002 — Process over Improvisation        El trabajo repetitivo debe ejecutarse mediante procesos diseñados previamente, no mediante improvisación constante.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gOy_V4JtXGHcsWGvE-OIl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1688.6024769607814,
      "y": 1811.8295982827908,
      "width": 795.367431640625,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 567038950,
      "version": 39,
      "versionNonce": 1026067622,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783648594727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CP-003 — Transformation over Collection        El objetivo no es\nacumular información, sino transformarla en conocimiento,\ncapacidades, activos y resultados.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CP-003 — Transformation over Collection        El objetivo no es acumular información, sino transformarla en conocimiento, capacidades, activos y resultados.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MRelz4-ehtj5ZXLJjitlf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1688.6024769607814,
      "y": 1969.9772195272703,
      "width": 778.9314575195312,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1858061690,
      "version": 32,
      "versionNonce": 788269030,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783648594727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CP-004 — Design before Execution        Pensar y diseñar un\nbuen sistema tiene más impacto que optimizar la ejecución de\ntareas individuales.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CP-004 — Design before Execution        Pensar y diseñar un buen sistema tiene más impacto que optimizar la ejecución de tareas individuales.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EjkppUtPRnPJXoC3icB5O",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1688.6024769607814,
      "y": 2128.12484077175,
      "width": 775.1513061523438,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 841279270,
      "version": 74,
      "versionNonce": 1732123430,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783648594727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CP-005 — Simplicity through Structure        La simplicidad no\nsurge de tener menos elementos, sino de una arquitectura\nclara y consistente.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CP-005 — Simplicity through Structure        La simplicidad no surge de tener menos elementos, sino de una arquitectura clara y consistente.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NJ7DBqOfUQPdZCDVLPi1S",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2827.4020124492085,
      "y": 1928.5172575618226,
      "width": 7.3079986572265625,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 537182970,
